    "In addition, the outlier pair removal module is embedded in many end-to-end models.",
    "The methods for removing outlier pairs are summarized as shown in Table 3.",
    "In point cloud registration based on correspondence relationships, rigid motion attitude estimation is generally the last stage of point cloud registration.",
